{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/rami-malek-model-video-game/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Rami Malek, Model Video Game yang Memerankan Freddie Mercury","content":"<p>Walaupun film “Bohemian Rhapsody” mendapatkan kritikan tajam, terutama di bagian akurasi sejarah (termasuk beberapa aspek penampilan anggota Queen yang tidak sesuai waktu penceritaan) namun nyatanya film ini tetap hits di pasaran. Disutradarai oleh Bryan Singer (dan konon sempat terjadi kericuhan internal antara Singer dengan <em>crew</em> dan aktor), film Bohemian Rhapsody yang merupakan produksi bersama antara Inggris dan Amerika Serikat tersebut sudah menghasilkan penjualan tiket hingga $ 145 Juta, dan masih mungkin akan bertambah, dari modal produksi yang ‘cuma’ $ 55 Jutaan saja.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51744\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51744\" data-attachment-id=\"51744\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-bohemianrhapsody/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-BohemianRhapsody.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RamiMalek-BohemianRhapsody\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Salah satu poster film “Bohemian Rhapsody” (Sumber gambar: MovieWeb)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-BohemianRhapsody-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-BohemianRhapsody.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51744\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-BohemianRhapsody.jpg\" alt=\"RamiMalek-BohemianRhapsody\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-BohemianRhapsody.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-BohemianRhapsody-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51744\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Salah satu poster film “Bohemian Rhapsody” (Sumber gambar: MovieWeb)</p></div>\n<p><strong>Baca juga: </strong><a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/bohemian-rhapsody-review-rami-malek/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bohemian Rhapsody: Transformasi Freddie Mercury Rami Malek Yang Sangat Jawara</a></p>\n<p>Selain kisah dan kontroversi yang mewarnai film Bohemian Rhapsody, perhatian publik juga tentu tertuju pada pemeran Freddie Mercury di film itu, yaitu aktor keturunan Mesir bernama Rami Malek.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51743\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51743\" data-attachment-id=\"51743\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-freddymercury/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-FreddyMercury.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RamiMalek-FreddyMercury\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Rami Malek &#038; Freddie Mercury (Sumber gambar: SmoothRadio)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-FreddyMercury-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-FreddyMercury.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51743\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-FreddyMercury.jpg\" alt=\"RamiMalek-FreddyMercury\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-FreddyMercury.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-FreddyMercury-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51743\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rami Malek &amp; Freddie Mercury (Sumber gambar: SmoothRadio)</p></div>\n<h2>Rami Malek, Aktor Muda Keturunan Mesir-Yunani</h2>\n<p>Rami Malek merupakan aktor muda yang tidak bisa disebut sebagai aktor “kemarin sore”. Malek lahir 12 Mei 1981 di Los Angeles Amerika Serikat dari orang tua keturunan Mesir-Yunani. Uniknya Rami punya saudara kembar bernama Sami yang berprofesi sebagai guru sekolah serta kakak bernama Yasmine yang seorang dokter medis.</p>\n<p>Tidak seperti dua saudaranya tadi, Rami memilih jalan seni sebagai hidup.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51742\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51742\" data-attachment-id=\"51742\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-rami/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Rami.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RamiMalek-Rami\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Rami Malek (Sumber gambar: Complex)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Rami-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Rami.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51742\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Rami.jpg\" alt=\"RamiMalek-Rami\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Rami.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Rami-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51742\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rami Malek (Sumber gambar: Complex)</p></div>\n<p>Karir seni akting Rami dimulai sekitar tahun 2004 selepas tamat kuliah seni di sebuah universitas di Indiana. Tentu saja karirnya dimulai dari peran-peran kecil, seperti di serial TV “Gilmore Girls”. Karir besar Rami Malek dimulai di film “Night at the Museum” (2006) dan dua sekuelnya tahun 2009 serta 2014.</p>\n<p>Perannya disana adalah sebagai… Fir’aun Ahkmenrah. Sebuah peran yang tentu saja cocok dengan postur dan profil penampilan seorang Rami Malek. Wajah khas Rami Malek memang mencerminkan penampilan seseorang dari Afrika ataupun Timur Tengah, karena memiliki darah keturunan Mesir.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51741\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51741\" data-attachment-id=\"51741\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-firaun/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Firaun.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RamiMalek-Fir&#8217;aun\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Rami Malek saat berperan sebagai Fir’aun Mesir (Sumber gambar: Pinterest)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Firaun-300x158.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Firaun.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51741\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Firaun.png\" alt=\"RamiMalek-Fir'aun\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Firaun.png 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Firaun-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51741\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rami Malek saat berperan sebagai Fir’aun Mesir (Sumber gambar: Pinterest)</p></div>\n<p>Malek juga pernah berperan sebagai antagonis pembom bunuh diri di serial TV “24” (2010). Sebuah peran <em>stereotype,</em> mengingat wajah Rami Malek mencitrakan orang Timur Tengah; yang identik dengan pembom bunuh diri. Malek mendapatkan pujian kritikus saat berperan sebagai Kopral Merriel ‘Snafu’ Shelton di mini-seri tentang Perang Dunia Kedua berjudul “The Pacific”. Bahkan salah satu produser dari mini-seri tersebut, aktor Tom Hanks, terkesan dengan penampilan Malek dan memberinya peran di filmnya bersama Julia Roberts berjudul “Larry Crowne” (2011).</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51740\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51740\" data-attachment-id=\"51740\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-jackbauer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-JackBauer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RamiMalek-JackBauer\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Beradu akting dengan Kiefer ‘Jack Bauer’ Sutherland di serial TV “24” (Sumber gambar: 24Spoilers)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-JackBauer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-JackBauer.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51740\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-JackBauer.jpg\" alt=\"RamiMalek-JackBauer\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-JackBauer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-JackBauer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51740\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Beradu akting dengan Kiefer ‘Jack Bauer’ Sutherland di serial TV “24” (Sumber gambar: 24Spoilers)</p></div>\n<p>Lebih sering mendapatkan peran pendukung, kita juga bisa melihat akting Rami Malek sebagai <em>vampire</em> di film “The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn – Part 2” tahun 2012. Atau di film <em>indie</em> “Short Term 12” (2013) di mana Rami beradu akting dengan aktris Brie Larson, yang tahun depan bisa disaksikan sebagai Captain Marvel di film Marvel Cinematic Universe “Captain Marvel” (2019).</p>\n<p><strong>Baca juga:</strong> <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/captain-marvel-akan-muncul-di-avengers-infinity-war-sudah-tahu-siapa-dia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Captain Marvel akan Muncul di Avengers: Infinity War! Sudah Tahu Siapa Dia?</a></p>\n<p>Tapi mungkin peran Rami Malek sebagai Elliot Alderson di serial TV “Mr. Robot” yang membuat sosoknya melejit tinggi?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51739\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51739\" data-attachment-id=\"51739\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-mrrobot/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Mrrobot.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RamiMalek-Mrrobot\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: MaximumMedia.ie&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Mrrobot-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Mrrobot.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51739\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Mrrobot.jpg\" alt=\"RamiMalek-Mrrobot\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Mrrobot.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-Mrrobot-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51739\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: MaximumMedia.ie</p></div>\n<p>Di Mr. Robot Rami berperan sebagai seorang ahli <em>cyber security</em> yang juga seorang <em>hacker</em> kawakan dan punya penyakit anti-sosial, depresi akut hingga sering berhalusinasi serta memiliki kepribadian ganda.</p>\n<p>Disini aktingnya menurut saya keren banget. Dengan tatapan yang sering terlihat kosong, <em>emotionless</em> dan <em>lifeless</em> namun punya skill komputer jaringan luar biasa, karakter Elliot dan Mr. Robot (apik diperankan oleh aktor lawas Christian Slater) merupakan energi mistis yang membuat serial Mr. Robot menarik. Apalagi dengan tema kekinian di bagian keamanan jaringan komputer (termasuk soal pencurian data pribadi secara online atau penggunaan uang digital yang nyaman namun sangat berbahaya jika diretas) akan membuat menonton Mr. Robot seru banget.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51738\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51738\" data-attachment-id=\"51738\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-christianslater/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-christianslater.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RamiMalek-christianslater\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Rami Malek bersama Christian Slater (Sumber gambar: USANetwork)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-christianslater-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-christianslater.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51738\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-christianslater.jpg\" alt=\"RamiMalek-christianslater\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-christianslater.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-christianslater-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51738\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rami Malek bersama Christian Slater (Sumber gambar: USANetwork)</p></div>\n<p>Kejeniusan Rami Malek di serial Mr. Robot diganjar dengan nominasi Dorian Award, Satellite Award, Golden Globe Award dan Screen Guild Award. Rami sendiri memenangkan penghargaan dari Critic’s Choice Television Award serta Primetime Emmy Award sebagai Aktor Utama Terbaik Serial Televisi dari perannya sebagai Elliot Alderson di serial Mr. Robot tersebut.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51737\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51737\" data-attachment-id=\"51737\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-pialaemmy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-PialaEmmy.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RamiMalek-PialaEmmy\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Rami Malek saat memenangkan Piala Emmy untuk Mr. Robot (Sumber gambar: Engadget)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-PialaEmmy-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-PialaEmmy.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51737\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-PialaEmmy.jpg\" alt=\"RamiMalek-PialaEmmy\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-PialaEmmy.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-PialaEmmy-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51737\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rami Malek saat memenangkan Piala Emmy untuk Mr. Robot (Sumber gambar: Engadget)</p></div>\n<h3>Rami Malek Pernah Menjadi Pengisi Suara dan Model Video Game</h3>\n<p>Selain berakting di serial TV dan film teatrikal, Malek juga pernah merambah area video game.</p>\n<p>Yaitu di game populer untuk konsol Xbox yang berjudul “Halo 2” (2004). Di sini dia berperan sebagai pengisi suara beberapa karakter. Sayang, peran tersebut tidak terlalu penting sehingga namanya tidak tertera di <em>credit title</em> Halo 2 sebagai bagian pengisi suara. Dia juga sempat mengisi suara karakter Tahno di game “The Legend of Korra” (2014).</p>\n<p>Baru di game horror PlayStation 4 berjudul “Until Dawn” (2015), Rami Malek berperan lebih besar karena selain suara, wajah dan seluruh bagian tubuhnya juga di-<em>capture</em> ke dalam <em>game</em> sebagai karakter bernama Joshua ‘Josh’ Washington. Jika kamu punya PS4 maka kamu perlu cobain<em> game</em> ini. Dengan gaya bercerita seperti film-film Hollywood era “t<em>een slasher horror movies”, game</em> Until Dawn memiliki banyak percabangan jalan cerita yang akan menentukan <em>ending game</em>. Pilih sendiri petualanganmu!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Game “Until Dawn”</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7ijBYjZ0e6s\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51736\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51736\" data-attachment-id=\"51736\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-gameuntildawn/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-GameUntilDawn.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"RamiMalek-GameUntilDawn\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Game “Until Dawn” juga dibintangi aktor/aktris Hollywood lain (Sumber gambar: WordPress)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-GameUntilDawn-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-GameUntilDawn.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51736\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-GameUntilDawn.jpg\" alt=\"RamiMalek-GameUntilDawn\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-GameUntilDawn.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-GameUntilDawn-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51736\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Game “Until Dawn” juga dibintangi aktor/aktris Hollywood lain (Sumber gambar: WordPress)</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q3DYAyv2Ics\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Trailer “Until Dawn”</strong></p>\n<p>Di film “Bohemian Rhapsody”, peran Rami Malek sebagai Freddie Mercury banyak menuai pujian.</p>\n<p>Berbagai komentar bernada positif tentang akting Rami sebagai karakter se-<em>flamboyant</em> Freddie Mercury banyak beredar di internet. Salah satu komentar mengatakan kalau “para pemain film Bohemian Rhapsody melakukan tugas mereka dengan baik; terutama sekali Rami Malek yang seakan-akan menghidupkan kembali Freddie ke dunia”.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51735\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51735\" data-attachment-id=\"51735\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/rami-malek-model-video-game/attachment/ramimalek-freddiemercury/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/RamiMalek-FreddieMercury.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quo